<h1 class="govuk-heading-l"><%= t('service.name') %></h1>

<p class="govuk-body">Use this service to manage the details of all initial teacher training (ITT) providers.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Who can use this service</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">You can use this service if you are a member of the Department for Education (DfE).</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Before you start</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  To access this service, you will be asked to sign in or create a DfE Sign-in account.
  DfE Sign-in is how training providers and other education organisations access DfE online services.
</p>

<%= govuk_start_button(text: "Sign in", href: root_path, classes: "govuk-!-margin-top-4") %>
